			<ol class="commentlist">
								<li class="comment byuser comment-author-jptjmj3 even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-440">
										<article id="div-comment-440" class="comment-body">
										<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<cite class="fn">jptjmj3</cite>						<time>
							June 11, 2014 at 1:55 am				
						</time>
					</div>
		
				<p>Alright, first things first. 4/10. We have had this model for three years for school, and on the first year, I was on the verge of breaking. The computer is clunky, the keyboard is cramped (Gives you arthritis), the mouse (If thats what you want to call it) is terrible, and the battery, ooh I could go on and on on that piece of garbage. Ive gone through, oh lets see here, *Talking to self* &#8220;One, five&#8230;&#8221; At least TEN batteries in three years! The locks on the bottom to keep it in don&#8217;t work properly and the battery lasts on power-saver 4 hours. Ok, now the good things about it: It works for any school uses, some basic games, (Minecraft, Torchlight, Spelunky, ect) and processes pretty fast. I would recommend this laptop to people who are dumb and low on money. Yeah, not a very good laptop&#8230;</p>
								</article>
						</li><!-- #comment-## -->
				<li class="comment byuser comment-author-sunnyboy88 odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-2883">
										<article id="div-comment-2883" class="comment-body">
										<div class="comment-author vcard">
												<cite class="fn">SunnyBoy88</cite>						<time>
							September 19, 2015 at 3:09 pm				
						</time>
					</div>
		
				<p>I find this notebook  7.5/10. I use it for traveling&#8230;.. super light weight, good for watching online movies n simple surfing net n some office app. </p>
<p>It is very affordable now&#8230;.simply up the ram to 8gb ram install win7 64bit plus any 7200rpm hard disk n you are good to go.</p>
<p>You can even run VM on this machine, tried Linux n Unix&#8230;no problem at all.</p>
<p>Cons &#8211;  Battery life is pathetic, mine last about 1hr for 4 cell battery but mine is a used battery so can&#8217;t complain much.If only IBM/Lenovo could invent a 12cell battery for this machine&#8230;.it would be a champion.</p>
								</article>
						</li><!-- #comment-## -->
